http://manpages.ubuntu.com/manpages/precise/man8/libvirtd.8.html

EXAMPLES

       To retrieve the version of libvirtd:

        # libvirtd --version
        libvirtd (libvirt) 0.8.2
        #

       To start libvirtd, instructing it to daemonize and create a PID file:

        # libvirtd -d
        # ls -la
        -rw-r--r-- 1 root root 6 Jul  9 02:40
        #

BUGS

       Please report all bugs you discover.  This should be done via either:

       a) the mailing list
           <http://libvirt.org/contact.html>

       or,

       b) the bug tracker
           <http://libvirt.org/bugs.html>

       Alternatively, you may report bugs to your software distributor /
       vendor.


